#!/usr/bin/env python3

"""

Sync AWS Security Groups from source to target (DR) with:

- Cross-account SG name normalization

- Idempotent SG creation

- Tag sync

- Ingress/Egress delta reconciliation

- Audit + JSON report

- Parallel reconciliation

- Rollback on first failure

- Dry-run / report-only / name-preview safety modes

Examples:

Dry run:

python sync_sg.py \

  --source-profile prod-profile \

  --source-region us-east-1 \

  --source-vpc-id vpc-aaaaaaaa \

  --target-profile dr-profile \

  --target-region us-east-2 \

  --target-vpc-id vpc-bbbbbbbb \

  --dry-run

Real execution:

python sync_sg.py \

  --source-profile prod-profile \

  --source-region us-east-1 \

  --source-vpc-id vpc-aaaaaaaa \

  --target-profile dr-profile \

  --target-region us-east-2 \

  --target-vpc-id vpc-bbbbbbbb \

  --workers 4 \

  --yes

"""

